y at the company=E2=80=99s 40th anniversary party, or thought of re-creatin=
g La C=C3=B4te Basque at the New York Public Library. Those ideas are very =
much driven by designers <b>Olympia Gayot</b> and <b>Brendon Babenzien </b>=
